Package: saeproj.multilevel
Title: Small Area Estimation via Multilevel Projection Estimator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Nazlya",
        family = "Rahma Susanto",
        email = "susantonazlya@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides tools for Small Area Estimation using a projection
    estimator with a linear mixed-effects working model. The main function
    fits a multilevel model to a smaller survey containing the response
    variable and auxiliary predictors, predicts outcomes in a larger
    projection dataset, and computes domain-level estimates with design-based
    residual bias correction.
